<p><a href="#sdfootnote37anc" name="sdfootnote37sym">37</a>Horobin narrows down Lichfield Cathedral as the likely center of production based on Doyle’s Cistercian identification, the linguistic markers from the West Midlands, and the size of the house necessary to support such an expensive undertaking.</p>
